
To install the cl-zip package in Debian GNU/Hurd:

# apt-get install cl-inflate cl-trivial-gray-streams cl-salza
# wget -c http://common-lisp.net/project/zip/zip.tgz
# cd /usr/share/common-lisp/source/
# tar zxvf zip.tgz
# cd zip
# patch -p1 < zip-other-streams.patch
# ln -sf /usr/share/common-lisp/source/zip/zip.asd /usr/share/common-lisp/systems/

